ft"}},{"element":".chat-panel__content-area","popover":{"title":"Replies and Announcements","description":"To answer one message without cluttering the chat, click Reply in thread — a side panel keeps that back-and-forth together, and a replies link reopens it later. Announcements show up here the moment they're posted, and also in read-only Broadcast channels. You write announcements from Admin, not from chat, and only admins and managers can post them.","side":"left"}},{"element":".chat-panel__channel-list","popover":{"title":"Unread, Mute, and Settings","description":"Each row shows how many messages you haven't read, and opening a conversation clears its count. Mute a busy channel from its row to turn off its alerts while staying in it. Click the gear on a channel to rename it, edit it, or leave — each person is a Member, an Admin, or the Owner.","side":"right"}}]}"""
