chat. Chat is where you receive and read announcements."},{"label":"Who can post","value":"Only admins and managers. For everyone else, announcements and broadcast channels are read-only."},{"label":"Who they reach","value":"The whole company, one department, or specific teams."},{"label":"Importance","value":"Info, Warning, or Critical."},{"label":"Acknowledgment","value":"Some announcements ask you to confirm you've read them."},{"label":"Templates and expiry","value":"Admins can reuse templates to write them faster, and an announcement can be set to expire on a date."}]},{"heading":"Channel Roles","items":[{"label":"Member","value":"Can read and post in the channel and mute their own alerts."},{"label":"Admin","value":"Can do everything a Member can, plus rename and edit the channel and manage it."},{"label":"Owner","value":"Has full control, including deleting the channel."}]},{"heading":"Times and Dates","items":[{"label":"Recent times","value":"'just now' under a minute, then '5m', '2h', '3d' for recent messages in your list."},{"label":"Older dates","value":"A full date shows for messages older than a week in your conversation list."},{"label":"Message time","value":"The time of day shows on each message."},{"label":"Day dividers","value":"'Today', 'Yesterday', or the full date appear between groups of messages."}]},{"heading":"Unread and Read","items":[{"label":"Top-bar chat number","value":"How many messages you haven't read across all your chats and channels. It updates the moment new messages arrive."},{"label":"Row number","value":"Unread count for a single chat or channel. It clears when you open that conversation."},{"label":"Marking read","value":"Just opening a conversation marks its messages as read."},{"label":"Mute","value":"Turns off a channel's alerts without taking you out of it."}]},{"heading":"Behind the Scenes","items":[{"label":"Instant delivery","value":"Messages, replies, and announcements arrive the moment they're sent — no need to refresh."},{"label":"Direct messages","value":"Your private chats load with a preview of the last message and how many are unread."},{"label":"Message history","value":"Older messages in a conversation load a page at a time as you scroll back."},{"label":"Sending","value":"You can send plain text, attach a file, or include a link to a record."},{"label":"Channels","value":"You can create channels, browse and join open ones, and mute or leave them."},{"label":"Threads","value":"Any message can start a thread, keeping side conversations tidy."},{"label":"Marking read","value":"Opening a chat or channel clears its unread count for you."},{"label":"Announcements","value":"Admins and managers post them, and you can confirm you've read the ones that ask."},{"label":"Files","value":"Attachments go out with your next message and can be opened right from the chat."},{"label":"Staying connected","value":"If your connection drops, chat reconnects on its own and catches you up."}]}]}"""
